Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H3133AE&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghouls!? Mysterious Snake-People Appear!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll feed my snakes well!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You trying to get yourself killed!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, pal...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I think someone's following us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that! Did we come\Nhere to photograph the ghost, or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A snake!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave if you want, but\NTakashi's counting on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised I'd get\Nhim a photo of the ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm glad I don't\Nhave a little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\i1}Closed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Turns out the victim\Nwas quite the athlete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,An obvious target for GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That blasted ghost...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This settles it, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The weird disappearances over the\Npast three months must be GOD's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And look at this, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tokyo suburbs are panicking\Nover this ghost business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The locals are too scared to\Neven set one foot in this spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that smell fishy to you,\Nchief? In this day and age?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You think GOD's got\Na secret base there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be careful. You're up\Nagainst a GOD monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, don't you want a coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-No thanks, I'm good.\N-But we just made some!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you g--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there? Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can\Ntrespass here and live?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Please\Nopen this gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster's after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:07:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What a peculiar day... I just let\Nsomeone in who said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's inside. Come on in...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Salamandra...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How goes your experiment to create snake-\Npeople with transfusions of your blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:08:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, it's almost complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent. Your snake-people's fangs will transform more humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...and soon all of Japan's\Ncitizens will be snake-people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, my precious\Nbabies! Feeding time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, eat up! Eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You big boys too, eat your fill!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cutie...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're cute too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mangrove snake! How\Nare you feeling today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with them...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,These marvellous snake-people\Nwere born from my own blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you here that\Nyou might join them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And now for the injection...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon...! There's a demon\Nhere! So scared... Help me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mad... He's been driven\Ntotally mad by fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew there was something\Nabout this cemetery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsumura, where's my\Nbrother? What happened!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared... Help me! So scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you can't go in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But my brother's--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:11:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No! There's something in this\Ngraveyard science can't explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-But my brother--\N-I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this place, foolish\Nhumans! Leave at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Disobey and my curse will\Nonly take more lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Run!!\N-Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Jin Keisuke, a\Nfriend of the X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider's friend...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider will save your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go home where it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me. Alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're GOD's new monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Salamandra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn to stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn to stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist! Are you\Ntrying to kill me too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All that matters is that he dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, don't lose your\Nhead. My goal is simple:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To defeat the X Rider.\NNow, retrieve his corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to tear it to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider died...\Ntrying to save my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda's actor also fell victim to a snake monster\Nin Kamen Rider Amazon. Talk about typecasting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That Salamandra's really something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But what was it that hurt her back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! She can't\Nstand her own reflection!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know her weakness,\Nthe rest is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need one of\Nmy bike's mirrors...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't the X Rider fall right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see a trace of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Great...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider's dead... But don't\Nworry big brother, I'll save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone in there must\Nknow where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for my big\Nbrother. Have you seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To think some food would\Njust bring itself to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out! Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd Jin Keisuke go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk! Where's Salamandra's base?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A python!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A scorpion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just a tortoise...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you--!? Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it! Turn this child\Ninto a snake-person!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:18:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, I'll let you\Ntest my snake-people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't panic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Takashi, jump in!\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A mirror of water!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain...! Help me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:20:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come out until\Nit's over, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end, X Rider!\NJoin my snake-people!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Komodo dragon, eat the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how you handle\NSalamandra's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a mirror!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.80,0:22:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm back to normal!\N-Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.40,0:22:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:22:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Takashi!\N-Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:23:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider foiled Salamandra's plot and\Nrestored the snake-people to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,0:23:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But his fight never ends. Go\Nfor it, Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.38,0:23:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,420)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.30,0:23:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fad(0,6)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD revives its past monsters and sends them after the\NX Rider, led by their Chief of Secret Police Apollo Geist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.40,0:23:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Faced with such overwhelming odds,\Nthe X Rider finds himself in a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Apollo Geist's Final All-Out Attack!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
